(241, 1, '2012-05-18 18:51:20', '2012-05-18 18:51:20', '<div>\r\n<div itemprop="description" data-expand-tooltip="Click to expand description">\r\n\r\nO Velejador Wilhelm Schurmann foi filmado por seu amigo Ivan Floater, surfando de Stand Up em um dia de ondas grandes, decorrentes de um swell na costa de Sta Catarina, mais preciso nos molhes de Laguna.\r\n\r\nTop windsurfer Wilhelm Schurmann BRA999, spent the month of May in his hometown Ibiraquera and when the winds were not up, he was out his SUP finding new spots around the Region. Schurmann got an amazing session in the piers of Laguna, where a long right brakes about 2km from the beach. Check out the images done by Ivan Flater of this day.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Wilhelm Schurmann BRA999, takes on the big waves at Laguna', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wilhelm-schurmann-bra999-takes-on-the-big-waves-at-laguna', '', '', '2013-06-18 18:55:13', '2013-06-18 18:55:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=241', 0, 'post', '', 0),
